67
00:09:50,970 --> 00:09:53,850
I can expect your support, right? Team Leader?

68
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:59,870
The person who brought up the talk concert at Korea Arts Middle School with Chris...

69
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:04,400
was you, Section Chief Park?

70
00:10:06,850 --> 00:10:11,880
All this time, Kyunghoo had been dealing business too meekly...

