72
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:18,160
- Section Chief... 
 - Joon Young is on a downward trajectory.

73
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:23,060
I'm simply telling you, you're also responsible.

74
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:36,610
Deputy Yoo Jin, when your maternity leave ends next month, you'll come back to us, right?

75
00:10:38,530 --> 00:10:40,100
This is delicious.

76
